author: woodall_aidan
title: Snape the great key chain
review: This is the only key chain from Lego that I own, and the best one in the world. Severus Snape is the perfect Lego figure to make a key chain of, other than Gregory Goyle (who they should make a key chain of). The figure is also the same figure as the Snape figure in the 4th edition Hogwarts Castle, which is cool. This key chain gets an overall 5/5 for coolness and rareness.
